channel.title: Vortex Remix - BobTheGUYYYYY
channel.description:
Here’s my entry for @HYDRANS’ contest. It was originally going to just be a remix, but I actually waited on it for a while and Hydrans ended up making it into a unicorn challenge! I was like “that’s convenient.”
Anyways, here it is! I hope you enjoy!
[![ISLPCA|500x500](upload://vS0fVygdFBdjx8QaFRjavvQ6oAk.png)](https://soundcloud.com/bobtheguyyyyy/vortex-remix-bobtheguyyyyy)
